sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as llama-stack-k8s-operator<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline<br/>Plugin Transforms
    participant LlamaServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant IngressCtrl as OpenShift Ingress<br/>Controller
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (CR change)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read operator-config ConfigMap<br/>(feature flags, image overrides)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Config data

    Operator->>Kustomize: Render base manifests
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: Apply plugins:<br/>1. Name prefix<br/>2. Namespace<br/>3. Field mutation<br/>4. NetworkPolicy transform
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered resources

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment,<br/>Service, SA, PVC, NP,<br/>PDB, HPA, RoleBinding
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resource status

    Note over Operator,LlamaServer: Status probing (after pod ready)

    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/health (8321/TCP HTTP)
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/providers (8321/TCP HTTP)
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/version (8321/TCP HTTP)
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Version info

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>(health, providers, version)

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 2: CA Bundle Aggregation

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read user CA bundle ConfigMap<br/>(DirectClient, uncached)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: User CA certificates
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>(DirectClient, uncached)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ODH CA certificates
    Operator->>Operator: Validate PEM/X.509 certs<br/>(10MB max, 1000 cert limit)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update managed<br/>{instance}-ca-bundle ConfigMap
    Note over LlamaServer: CA bundle mounted at<br/>/etc/ssl/certs/ca-bundle/<br/>SSL_CERT_FILE set

    Note over Client,LlamaServer: Flow 3: External Client Access (exposeRoute=true)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Ingress resource
    Client->>IngressCtrl: HTTP request (80/TCP)
    IngressCtrl->>LlamaServer: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>(8321/TCP HTTP)
    LlamaServer-->>IngressCtrl: Response
    IngressCtrl-->>Client: HTTP response
